Second Department,

July, 1957

(July 1, 1957) A. George Brown et al., Appellants, et al., Plaintiffs, v. Gene Williams, Respondent.

Motion referred to the court that rendered the decision. Present — Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Murphy, Ughetta and Kleinfeld, JJ. Motion for reargument denied, without costs. Motion for leave to appeal to the Court of Appeals denied. Present — Wenzel, Acting P. J., Murphy, Ughetta and Kleinfeld, JJ.; Beldock, J., not voting. [See 3 A D 2d 939.]
